fields.title: Hey I noticed you assigned me to cryocore
fields.description:
I hate hate hate hate hate hate hate cryocore and need opticool because I am using the optical setup that is in 325. Typing here is kind of cathartic. It's like I am writing in a diary.
Dear diary,
I still don't have approval to use the dewar filler. I really really don't wanna either. It's a bureaucratic type thing tbh, getting approval and room access and official training. And I barely use it. Other people empty half the tank every few days. It's loud and cold and uncomfortable. 
-Nate
